OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779045070
OL,3,CPolice share breakdown of arrests made
OL,4,Cat two rival London protests
OL,6,FPolice have shared a break down of 43
OL,7,Farrests made during two rival protests
OL,8,Fthat brought tens of thousands of
OL,9,Fdemonstrators into London on Saturday.
OL,11,FAbout 60,000 people are estimated to
OL,12,Fhave joined Tommy Robinson's Unite the
OL,13,FKingdom march in the capital, and
OL,14,Fbetween 15,000 and 20,000 attended the
OL,15,FNakba Day rally in support of
OL,16,FPalestine, Met Police said.
OL,18,FOverall, there were 43 arrests on the
OL,19,Fday, with 20 linked to the Unite the
OL,20,FKingdom protest and 12 with the Nakba
OL,21,Fprotest, the force said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
