OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779045070
OL,3,CPolice share breakdown of arrests made
OL,4,Cat two rival London protests
OL,6,FThere were 11 arrests of hate crime
OL,7,Frelated offences, nine of which were
OL,8,Faffiliated to the Unite the Kingdom
OL,9,Fmarch and two with the pro-Palestine
OL,10,Fevent.
OL,12,FA further seven hate crime offences
OL,13,Ffrom the Nakba protest are under
OL,14,Finvestigation with outstanding
OL,15,Fsuspects, police said.
OL,17,FThere were also 11 arrests linked to
OL,18,Fneither group or their affiliation has
OL,19,Fnot been confirmed, the Met said, with
OL,20,Ftwo of them also later de-arrested.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
