OL,3,CPolice share breakdown of arrests made
OL,4,Cat two rival London protests
OL,6,FUnite the Kingdom: 20 linked arrests
OL,8,FNakba Day: 12 linked arrests
OL,10,FNo affiliation or not confirmed: 11
OL,11,Farrests
OL,13,FAround 4,000 police officers were on
OL,14,Fduty during the protests, including
OL,15,Fhundreds drafted in from other parts
OL,16,Fof the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
