CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779045070
OL,3,CPolice share breakdown of arrests made
OL,4,Cat two rival London protests
OL,6,FArmoured vehicles, police horses,
OL,7,Fdogs, drones and helicopters were
OL,8,Fdeployed and live facial recognition
OL,9,Fsystems were in use for the first time
OL,10,Fin a protest policing operation.
OL,12,FOrganisers of the Nakba Day rally
OL,13,Festimated at least a quarter of a
OL,14,Fmillion people attended, while
OL,15,FRobinson claimed "millions of
OL,16,Fpatriots" had been at Unite the
OL,17,FKingdom.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
