OL,3,CPolice share breakdown of arrests made
OL,4,Cat two rival London protests
OL,6,FSpeakers at the Unite the Kingdom
OL,7,Frally included media personality Katie
OL,8,FHopkins and actors Laurence Fox and
OL,9,FTamer Hassan, as well as former
OL,10,FConservative MP Andrew Bridgen and
OL,11,FPolish politician Dominik Tarczynski.
OL,13,FTarczynski, who spoke via video link,
OL,14,Fclaimed he had been banned from
OL,15,Fentering the UK by Keir Starmer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
