PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779045070
OL,3,CPolice share breakdown of arrests made
OL,4,Cat two rival London protests
OL,6,FMPs Jeremy Corbyn, Diane Abbott,
OL,7,FApsana Begum and Zarah Sultana all
OL,8,Fspoke at the pro-Palestine event, with
OL,9,Fmany of them making passionate
OL,10,Fdeclarations against racism,
OL,11,Fislamophobia and antisemitism.
OL,13,FUnder new guidance, prosecutors in the
OL,14,FUK have been told to consider whether
OL,15,Fprotest placards, banners and chants
OL,16,Fviewed on social media may amount to
OL,17,Foffences of stirring up hatred during
OL,18,Fthe rallies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
