FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779045070
OL,3,CPolice share breakdown of arrests made
OL,4,Cat two rival London protests
OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,7,Fsaid the revised advice was designed
OL,8,Fto reflect "the changing international
OL,9,Fcontext" and follows separate guidance
OL,10,Fconcerning the fast-tracking of hate
OL,11,Fcrime prosecutions issued earlier this
OL,12,Fmonth.
OL,14,FIt tells prosecutors to take account
OL,15,Fof the wider context around protests,
OL,16,Fincluding heightened tensions linked
OL,17,Fto national or international events.
